description:
Drew Hernandez fills in for Jack Posobiec to discuss the deep state! Somehow, after Trump got permission for a special master to oversee the documents seized in the raid, the contents of the top secret documents were leaked to the Washington Post - go figure. War Room’s Steve Bannon said “they’re coming after all of us,” after the New York state indictment; Drew analyzes why the deep state is attempting to shut Bannon down. A Delaware court denied the motion to delay the Musk-Twitter trial; however, the judge ruled that Elon Musk is allowed to use the Twitter whistleblower claims against the social media technocracy. SHADE WAR UPDATE: the Obamas visited the White House causing Biden to camp due to lingering tensions; everyone knows who’s actually quarterbacking (hint: it’s not Biden).
